  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action that provokes attacks of opportunity, you can expend 1 point of mental focus to unleash a ray of pure energy as a ranged touch attack. This ray has a range of 30 feet. The ray deals an amount of energy damage equal to 1d6 points + 1d6 points for every 2 occultist levels you possess beyond 1st (2d6 at 3rd level, 3d6 at 5th, and so on, to a maximum of 10d6 at 19th level).</p>\n<p>When you unleash an energy ray, you must decide what type of damage it deals (acid, cold, electricity, or fire).</p>"
